# MyDiary

MyDiary is a simple API allowing users to register, login and create, update, 
delete diary entries and descriptions

## Register [/api/v1/register]

### Register a new user [POST]
You may register a new user using this action. It takes a JSON
object containing a first name, last name, email and password

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "f_name": "Ronald",
            "l_name": "Toraac",
            "email": "rtorac@gmail.com",
            "password": "secret"
            
        }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /api/v1/register

    + Body

            {
                "Info": "User successfully registered",
            }

## Login [/api/v1/login]            

### Login a user [POST]

You may login a user using this action. It takes a JSON
object containing an email and password

+ Request (application/json)

        {
            "email": "rtorac@gmail.com",
            "password": "secret"
            
        }

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /api/v1/login

    + Body

