            }

## Add Diary [/api/v1/diary]            

### Add a diary entry [POST]

You add a diary using this action. It takes a JSON
object containing a diary name and
Authorization token in header

+ Request (application/json)

    + Headers

            Authorization: token
    + Body

            {
                "name": "Rally Uganda",
            }

+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /api/v1/diary

    + Body

            {
                'Info': 'Diary successfully added',
            }
    
## Retrieve Diary's [/api/v1/]  
### Retrieve diary entries [GET]

You retrieve diary entries using this action. 
Request contains Authorization token in header

    + Headers

            Authorization: token

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Headers

            Location: /api/v1/diary

    + Body
            
            [
                {
                    "My Diary entries": [
                        {
                            "Date Modified": "null",
                            "Date created": "Sun, 22 Jul 2018 13:49:27 GMT",
                            "id": 1,
                            "name": "Rally Uganda"
                        },
                        {
                            "Date Modified": "null",
                            "Date created": "Sun, 22 Jul 2018 16:49:27 GMT",
                            "id": 1,
                            "name": "Racing Kenya"
